    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at Gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model adequately predicts relative hemolysis index with mean error of 8.3%, within acceptable bounds for comparative device evaluation. RH < 1 criterion met across all 5 operating points. Model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
